<http://drug.uk/usage/renal-impairment/614db87c-8687-466f-92b9-da0d66f9372b> <http://drug.uk/model/patientCondition> "RenalImpairment" .
<http://drug.uk/usage/renal-impairment/614db87c-8687-466f-92b9-da0d66f9372b> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> " Accumulation of sodium from injection can occur in patients with renal failure.\nWith intravenous use:\nHigh doses may cause nephrotoxicity or neurotoxicity.\nDose adjustments\nIn adults:\nReduce dose or increase dose interval if creatinine clearance less than 10 mL/minute (consult product literature).\nIn children:\nExpert sources advise use normal dose every 8 hours if estimated glomerular filtration rate less than 10 mL/minute/1.73 m^2." .
<http://drug.uk/usage/renal-impairment/614db87c-8687-466f-92b9-da0d66f9372b> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://drug.uk/model/Usage> .
